creator: IN THE LAB
descriptionHtml:
We The Culture, define the future and pave the way for the next generation. You each represent In The Lab in your own unique way, which drives us to move forward as your cultural leaders. Come together and showcase your journey of being In The Lab, on the road to achieving your 10,000 hours of greatness.

In The Lab is one of the fastest growing social media & e-commerce brands in the world, growing bigger every day thanks to our loyal family (you). This app is here to make your shopping experience with us as convenient and enjoyable as possible.

Make sure to follow us on social media and tag @inthelablifestyle to show us rockin' your gear to be featured.

Instagram: @devinthelab @inthelablifestyle @navinitl
Twitter: @devinthelab
Facebook: @ten000hours
Website: www.ten000hours.com

title: In The Lab

creator: IN THE LAB
descriptionHtml:
In The Lab is based on the concept of 10,000 hours. We say that it takes 10,000 hours of dedicated, focused and committed practice to master your craft. Every day we're all In The Lab working together to achieve our own personal feats of mastery and greatness.

We want to push people to achieve multiple breakthroughs within their lifetime. Breakthroughs are key components to growth, building confidence and taking a positive step forward in life. These are life-changing moments that act for the better and have an impact on the future. Over the years In The Lab has built an amazing community of individuals around the world who believe in and preach our message. This has allowed people to come together to work on their goals, creating an online family that spans the entire world.
